{"tid":478461,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"四年啦...","createTime":"2017-11-24T05:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T05:57:07.000Z","uid":139089,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a7be35267d23c320e375cbb6d447d480fdfcbaa0","tid":478461,"uid":139089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:45:39.000Z","msg":"真係無地方呻先上黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拍拖四年，對方係世叔伯個女<br />\n我唔係叻，對比起佢屋企更加唔係有錢<br />\n以佢條件，要搵個更好既公子哥兒根本一d都唔難<br />\n但佢都不離不棄跟左我四年<br />\n本身我都諗住年尾就求婚，<br />\n但早兩日因為我ex仲有聯絡又嗌交，而家仲話要分開冷靜下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1924dcd5e718dc210ebe4af8a2cdd1238cf01e0b","tid":478461,"uid":32446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:57:07.000Z","msg":"咁點解明知嗌交仲要同ex聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}